# Design documents

Follow [.notebook/06_design/README.md](../../.notebook/06_design/README.md).

## Basic vs Detail

| Type | Folder | Skills |
|------|--------|--------|
| Basic | `00_project/`, `01_functions/` | `basic-design` |
| Detail | `02_screens/`, `03_objects/`, `04_integrations/`, `05_batches/`, `06_logic/` | `detail-design` |

## Rules

- Copy from `_*.template.md`; remove `_` prefix in new filenames
- Link design files from `backlogs/task-{id}/README.md` **Design** section
- Do not duplicate full acceptance criteria — reference backlog task
- Comments in code: English. Design docs for PM/client: project language (often Vietnamese)
